Book Management System
------------------------------------
Overview

The Book Management System is a software application designed to manage books efficiently. It provides functionality for adding, updating, deleting, and retrieving book records.
----------------------------------
Features

Add new books with details such as title, author, and genre.

Update book information.

Delete books from the system.

Retrieve book details based on various criteria.

User-friendly interface.
--------------------------------

